{"tid":2345978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"霸王級寒流、限電夾擊！中国奴工只能開電腦摸黑工作","createTime":"2020-12-30T03:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T04:27:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5718b20d36eca33b6e6073f7c291b16700ac39d7","tid":2345978,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"霸王級寒流今明（30、31）兩日將南下至中國，中國中央氣象台時隔4年再次發布「寒潮橙色預警」，預估約8成的國土將進入「急凍」狀態。近日中國多個地區實施限電令，浙江甚至被要求氣溫3℃以下才能開空調，面對霸王級寒流，中國內部如何應對令人關注。<br />\n<br />\n據中國中國天氣網，昨（29）日寒潮主體（西伯利亞冷氣團）前鋒抵達南嶺，使大陸中東部大部分地區急速降溫。12月30日至31日中國將迎來今年入冬以來最強寒流，部分地區「斷崖式」降溫，25個省會級城市預計將在31日創下今年冬天最低溫。中國中央氣象台29日即發布最高級別的寒潮橙色預警，今（30）日續發警報。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.nownews.com/nn_media/thumbnail/2020/12/1609228162180-1fb7f26eb7f04cda92fe88449ca91fe1-800x503.jpg?unShow=false\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.nownews.com%2Fnn_media%2Fthumbnail%2F2020%2F12%2F1609228162180-1fb7f26eb7f04cda92fe88449ca91fe1-800x503.jpg%3FunShow%3Dfalse&h=141e324c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在霸王級寒流的侵襲下，中國至少20多個省市傳出限電、限氣、限產，微博上流傳的通知顯示，浙江義烏市路燈關閉、溫州禁止在3℃以上開空調；湖南長沙禁止使用電梯、地下室照明；山西省運城市綠源天然氣公司發函全縣所有天然氣用戶分時段供氣；河北省華鋼燃氣集團停止向工業用戶供應天然氣。<br />\n<br />\n微博上有網友反應「今年用電這麼緊張嗎？連學校都要限電了（汗顏）」、「行政單位限電不能開空調不能烤火」。根據麓谷訊息港物業運營中心28日的通知，電力公司將於霸王級寒流2日對園區進行用電負荷控制，由於大樓停電不少上班族開始提早放假，但也有人待的單位必須用電腦「摸黑上班」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.nownews.com/nn_media/thumbnail/2020/12/1609295115035-511bbf395ded49b8983429f9e1c47423-749x172.png?unShow=false\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.nownews.com%2Fnn_media%2Fthumbnail%2F2020%2F12%2F1609295115035-511bbf395ded49b8983429f9e1c47423-749x172.png%3FunShow%3Dfalse&h=010feb16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.nownews.com/nn_media/thumbnail/2020/12/1609295129925-766ad37d26fa46819e315a71a9914524-752x399.png?unShow=false\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.nownews.com%2Fnn_media%2Fthumbnail%2F2020%2F12%2F1609295129925-766ad37d26fa46819e315a71a9914524-752x399.png%3FunShow%3Dfalse&h=4caf02f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖南科技大學28日也發出停電通知，指晚上10時30分至凌晨零時，第十教學樓東附樓、化學樓、化工樓、理論有機化學與功能分子教育部重點實驗室、體育館、物理樓、生物樓、生物園、第一田徑場停電，電梯、網路隨停電而中斷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.nownews.com/nn_media/thumbnail/2020/12/1609295236160-1fe4ef9c3978487484853074d371e79d-690x164.png?unShow=false\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.nownews.com%2Fnn_media%2Fthumbnail%2F2020%2F12%2F1609295236160-1fe4ef9c3978487484853074d371e79d-690x164.png%3FunShow%3Dfalse&h=bd116d89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.nownews.com/nn_media/thumbnail/2020/12/1609295291349-8a08956670414cf783c3146d728df344-635x515.jpg?unShow=false\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.nownews.com%2Fnn_media%2Fthumbnail%2F2020%2F12%2F1609295291349-8a08956670414cf783c3146d728df344-635x515.jpg%3FunShow%3Dfalse&h=751f733d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.nownews.com/nn_media/thumbnail/2020/12/1609295388361-a48ebf9adba34929821145bd920e147c-687x488.jpg?unShow=false\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.nownews.com%2Fnn_media%2Fthumbnail%2F2020%2F12%2F1609295388361-a48ebf9adba34929821145bd920e147c-687x488.jpg%3FunShow%3Dfalse&h=740f256a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.nownews.com/nn_media/thumbnail/2020/12/1609295388361-638ca806526543f9b3c63a12003dd525-681x291.jpg?unShow=false\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.nownews.com%2Fnn_media%2Fthumbnail%2F2020%2F12%2F1609295388361-638ca806526543f9b3c63a12003dd525-681x291.jpg%3FunShow%3Dfalse&h=296cbb24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/5151742\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F5151742&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGfPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=cae4e647\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/5151742</a>"},{"pid":"8a224d223efe8f33e98291a